---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Vizino AI" 
  description="Learn how Vizino AI collects, uses, and protects your personal information and uploaded content."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: February 9, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <p class="intro">
          Vizino AI respects your privacy. This page summarizes how we handle the data you share while using our interior design visualization platform.
        </p>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>1. What We Collect</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Account info:</strong> Name, email handled via secure processors.</li>
            <li><strong>Uploads:</strong> Room photos, custom materials, prompts, and AI results stored per project.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage signals:</strong> IP, device/browser, feature usage and errors.</li>
            <li><strong>Optional beta feedback:</strong> Comments, bug reports, and adoption metrics.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>2. How We Use It</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide the service: organize images and materials, run AI generations, and power "Help Me Write".</li>
            <li>Improve the product: analyze usage to enhance features (without training on your private uploads).</li>
            <li>Communicate: reply to support, notify you about updates, and send optional marketing.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>3. Sharing & Protection</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Shared only with trusted vendors (cloud hosts, AI infrastructure, analytics, email) under strict contracts.</li>
            <li>Encryption (TLS in transit, encryption at rest), access controls, monitoring.</li>
            <li>We do not sell your personal data or expose uploads without permission.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>4. Retention & Rights</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Account and upload data stays until you delete it.</li>
            <li>Export projects/prompts/images via the platform or by contacting contact@vizino.ai.</li>
            <li>Update or delete data anytime; request account removal if desired (brief recovery window may apply).</li>
            <li>Opt out of marketing anytime; service-critical messages (billing/security) remain active.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>5. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Essential cache keep the platform functional; analytics data help us improve.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>6. Contact</h2>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <p><strong>Vizino AI</strong></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@vizino.ai">contact@vizino.ai</a></p>
          </div>
          <p>We aim to reply within 30 days.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="legal-footer">
          <p>Effective February 9, 2026.</p>
          <p><a href="/">Return to Home</a> | <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .legal-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .legal-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-indigo);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--brand-indigo-light);
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
  }

  .legal-section h3 {
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }

  .legal-section p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
  }

  .legal-section strong {
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    color: var(--brand-indigo-dark);
  }

  .contact-info {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .legal-footer {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-4xl);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .legal-footer p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .legal-footer a {
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    margin: 0 var(--spacing-md);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
    }

    .legal-header {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .legal-section {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    }

    .legal-section h3 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    }
  }
</style>
